<view class="page wallet-page">
  <view wx:if="{{needsLogin}}" class="card login-empty">
    <text class="login-empty-title">登录后查看积分与订单</text>
    <text class="login-empty-desc">充值记录、消费明细和积分余额都会跟随账号同步。</text>
    <button class="login-empty-btn" bindtap="goLogin">去登录</button>
  </view>

  <block wx:else>
    <view class="balance-card">
      <view class="balance-label">我的积分</view>
      <view class="balance-value">{{creditBalance}} <text class="balance-unit">积分</text></view>
      <text class="balance-desc">生成 1 张写真通常消耗 2-3 积分，以模板实际标价为准。</text>
      <text class="balance-mark">P</text>
    </view>

    <view class="section-title">充值套餐</view>
    <view class="package-grid">
      <button
        wx:for="{{packages}}"
        wx:key="id"
        class="package-card {{item.id === selectedPackageId ? 'active' : ''}}"
        data-id="{{item.id}}"
        bindtap="selectPackage"
      >
        <text class="package-price">{{item.priceLabel}}</text>
        <text class="package-credits">{{item.creditsLabel}}</text>
        <text class="package-bonus">{{item.bonusLabel}}</text>
      </button>
    </view>

    <button class="recharge-btn" bindtap="rechargeNow">立即充值</button>

    <view class="wallet-note">
      <text>支付接通前不会生成虚假订单。</text>
      <text>充值成功后，订单和流水会分别在“我的”页查看。</text>
      <text>生成失败会自动退回对应积分。</text>
    </view>
  </block>
</view>
